==English==

===Pronunciation===
*/ˈtreɪdmɑː(r)k/, /"treIdmA:(r)k/
*{{audio|en-us-trademark.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''trademark'''  (''plural:'' '''[[trademarks]]''')
# A [[word]], [[symbol]], or [[phrase]] used to identify a particular company's product and differentiate it from other companies' products.  Indicated by the symbol [[%E2%84%A2|&trade;]], when registered with a government authority it is sometimes indicated by the symbol [[&reg;]].

